<refentry id="bif.NodeValue" xreflabel="NodeValue">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>NodeValue</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>NodeValue</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>NodeValue</refname>
<refpurpose>
Returns the expected payoff to a player of being at a node
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
NodeValue[profile->BEHAV, player->EFPLAYER, node->NODE] =: NUMBER 
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>NodeValue</function>
returns the expected payoff to <parameter>player</parameter> at
<parameter>node</parameter>, given
that all players are following <parameter>profile</parameter>.
</para>
</refsect1>

